<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>242</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hungun Lalpa hehpih-
 Te'n kipah la sau un;
 Lung kiguolin la sau unla, (2)
 Lalchutphah kimvel un. (2)

[V2]
 Zion lam zuon I hiu,
 Khawpi hawih, Khawpi hawih tak;
 Chunglam Zion zuon I hiu ui,
 Pathien khawpi hawih tak mai chuh.

[V3]
 2. Pathien he ngeilo te'n,
 La sakding niel mahleu;
 Van Lalpen chate haw vang chun (2)
 Kipahna la sai tiu (2)

[V4]
 3. Zion tang chun thil ki -
 Pah um tampi ei tun;
 Van gam tuol I tun mau inle (2)
 Sana tuol len ma'n le (2)

[V5]
 4. Kipahna la sai tiu,
 Luonthi cheng le hul hen;
 Immanuel gam zuon I hiu (2)
 Chunglam khawvel nuom zaw (2)</lyrics>
<title>WE'RE MARCHING TO ZION</title>
</song>